{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/DeclarationAccessibility\/documentation\/DeclarationAccessibility","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a library, exposed as a Swift Package, which will help you to display a legal accessibility statement for your application."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"tip","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Feel free to submit pull requests if you can improve the support of any platforms!"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"Tip"},{"anchor":"How-to-use-the-library","level":2,"text":"How to use the library","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can integrate the dedicated "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":" in your app, e.g. in about pages:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"with local HTML file:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["StatementView(xmlFileName: fileName, theme: .orange, localURL: someURL)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or loading external HTML page:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["StatementView(xmlFileName: fileName, theme: .orange, remoteUrl: someURL, useWebView: true)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"where:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"fileName","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" is the name of the XML file containing the results of the accessibility audits"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"someURL"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" can be an absolute URL of an HTML file displaying a detailed page, or an external HTML page"}]}]}]}